snippet.title: Final Nights 4: Fates Entwined | Final Trailer
snippet.description:
The untold stories of Final Nights
In Final Nights 4 you will explore the original Fredbear's Family Diner and much more from 2 different perspectives.

Follow the game here!
https://gamejolt.com/games/FinalNights4/267878

Big thanks to Hyperdan and Tia Morrell for helping me figure out what to do with this trailer. 
Music by Caspar https://twitter.com/inthezonee
